Definition: any of a group of synthetic steroid hormones used to stimulate muscle and bone growth
Example: more than 100 have been developed and each requires a prescription to be used legally in the United States; sometimes used illicitly by athletes to increase their strength
Synonyms: steroid_hormone, any, of, a, group, synthetic, steroid, hormones, used, to, stimulate, muscle, and, bone, growth, more, than, have, been, developed, each, requires, prescription, be, legally, in, the, United, States, sometimes, illicitly, by, athletes, increase, their, strength
Category: noun.substance
